cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.SI, cs.SY 

The paper proposes a new technique for improving the accuracy of building demand forecasting, which involves machine learning and artificial intelligence. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves neural networks and recurrent models, which are commonly used in sub-categories such as cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). Finally, the paper deals with forecasting and prediction, which falls under the sub-category cs.SY (Systems and Control).
